CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1951, pg. 32 reads: "Relatives Greet Graduate - Soquoyah L. Payne, who was graduated from the college at Pitt is greeted by his mother, Mrs. Roceania Payne, left, and his wife, Mildred."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of University of Pittsburgh graduate Soquoyah L. Payne, standing between Roceania Payne, mother, left, and Mildred Payne, wife, right, standing on sidewalk in front of lawn, with Mellon Institute in background, Oakland
